d \"what if we could milk a bean?\" Then they actually figured out how to do that. Science can be beautiful sometimes.','legume/bean-milk',NULL,NULL,106,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(216,'Magic Bean Milk',NULL,'legume/bean-milk-magic',NULL,NULL,107,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(217,'Berry Pancakes',NULL,'bread/pancakes-blueberry',NULL,NULL,108,20,NULL,140,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(218,'Red Pancakes',NULL,'bread/pancakes-red',NULL,NULL,109,20,NULL,141,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(219,'Naner Pancakes','ohmygoshohmygoshohmygosh! IT\'S GOT WHOLE SLICES OF NANER IN IT!! ♥','bread/pancakes-naner',NULL,NULL,110,20,NULL,142,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(220,'Slice of Blackberry Pie','Oh no! Hurry up and eat it! Its juices are getting everywhere; it\'s gonna make the crust all sooooogggyyyyyyy!!!!!','dessert/pie-slice-blackberry',NULL,NULL,111,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(221,'Slice of Red Pie','Ooh, and it\'s still got some of the skins in there, too? Nice!','dessert/pie-slice-red',NULL,NULL,112,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(222,'Slice of Chocolate Cream Pie','Chocolate Cream Pie is SO good. Like: _really_ good. Like, I\'m not gonna say that you should absolutely, 100%, and without question make love to the first Slice of Chocolate Cream Pie you can get your hands on, but I\'m not gonna say you _shouldn\'t_, either.','dessert/pie-slice-chocolate',NULL,NULL,113,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(223,'Pie Recipes',NULL,'book/pie','[[\"Read\", \"pieRecipes/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"pieRecipes/#/upload\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(224,'Crazy-hot Torch','This magically-enchanted torch is strong enough to _shape metal_, and _pierce the unending darkness of the Umbral Storm!!_\n\nNeat-o!','tool/torch/crazy-hot',NULL,24,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,660,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(225,'Hakuna Frittata','Hakuna!\r\n\r\nFrittata!\r\n\r\nHakuna!\r\n\r\nFrittata!','fritt