usly _way_ better.\n\nI mean: c\'mon! They\'re _yellow!_','tool/scissors/yellow',NULL,29,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(235,'Green Scissors',NULL,'tool/scissors/green',NULL,30,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(236,'Hourglass','Wait, I don\'t get it. It\'s just a stopwatch but, like, way worse, right?','trinket/hourglass',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(237,'Magic Hourglass','Just as energy and matter are interchangeable, so, some wizards say, are space and time. This hourglass operates on that principle, converting space into time.\n\nAs for the health effects of exposure to the anti-dark energy that\'s created as a byproduct of this process, that\'s a topic of active study, particularly among members of [High Impact](/poppyopedia/guild/7).','trinket/hourglass-magic','[[\"Shatter\", \"magicHourglass/#/shatter\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,8,NULL,NULL,40,0,NULL,0,10),(238,'Garden Shovel','Respect the shovel, for it has seen things. It knows the whispers of the weeds and the skeletons in your compost.','tool/shovel/garden',NULL,31,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(239,'Chocomilk','Crafted with the finest island ingredients, squeezed from the finest island goats.','animal/milk-chocolate',NULL,NULL,116,7,36,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(240,'Milk: The Book',NULL,'book/milk','[[\"Read\", \"milkBook/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"milkBook/#/upload\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(241,'Straw Broom','Well. It\'s useful if you need to sweep, I guess?','tool/broom/straw',NULL,32,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,300,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(242,'Witch\'s Broom','With this broom, you\'ll be able to fly like a rabbit from a catapult.\r\n\r\n<small>(No rabbits were harmed in the making of this item description.)</small>','tool/broom/witchs',NULL,33,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,660,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(243,'Brownie','Er, but not Brownie, as in the faefolk; Brownie, as in the food! The edible kind of Brownie! Well, I mean, I guess if you\'re a Terrasque, both are edible, but I\'m assuming you\'re not a Terrasque, if for no other reason than that Terrasques don\'t read.','bread/brownie',NULL,NULL,117,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(244,'Moth','According to one tale, a young man fell in love with the moon and was turned into a moth, forever drawn to her light but never able to reach her.','bug/moth','[[\"Squish\", \"bug/#/squish\"], [\"Release to the Moon\", \"releaseMoths\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,0,1),(245,'Onion Rings','The first time I bit into an Onion Ring, it was like the humble onion had thrown off its earthy robe and donned a shimmering golden dress, and I was like: \"damn, son, that\'s a fine dress,\" and the Onion Ring was like, \"boy, I know it.\"\n\nYou know how it is.','veggie/onion-rings',NULL,NULL,118,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(246,'Orange Fish','Surprisingly sweet!','animal/meat/fish-orange',NULL,NULL,119,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(247,'Heavy Hammer','This thing is WAY heavier than it looks! Like, probably about 20 times heavier!','tool/hammer/heavy',NULL,34,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(248,'Spicy Peps',NULL,'fruit/peppers-spicy',NULL,NULL,120,2,12,NULL,30,0,17,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(249,'Shakshouka','What _type_ of food is Shakshouka, really? I mean, it\'s not, you know, _cake_. It\'s not - I dunno - salad. What is it? Soup? It\'s not soup. (Or is it?) I dunno, man. Whatever it is, it\'s delicious as hell. (Wait... is \"hell\" delicious?! Shakshouka, you pose far more questions than you answer!)','soup/shakshouka',NULL,NULL,121,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(250,'Basement Blueprint','Somehow, simply reading this blueprint grants you an enormous basement!\r\n\r\nI\'m starting to think there might be something magical going on on this island...','note/blueprint-basement','[[\"Read\", \"basementBlueprint\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,90,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(251,'Coffee Yogurt','I feel like I haven\'t seen Coffee Yogurt in the grocery stores for a while now. Is it still a thing? I mean, _I_ think it\'s one of the most vile creations of humankind, but, you know, I\'m sure _some_ people liked it. And miss it. (Somehow.)','yogurt/coffee',NULL,NULL,122,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(252,'Green Gummies',NULL,'candy/gummy/green',NULL,NULL,123,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(253,'Tentacle','It\'s a perfectly normal tentacle that occasionally waves hello. Your Lolligovore pets insist this is the best part.','animal/meat/tentacle',NULL,NULL,124,13,32,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(254,'Chili Calamari','Delicious!','animal/meat/tentacle-chilli',NULL,NULL,125,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(255,'Cheese','\"No matter how hard you work, you\'ll never be as famous as cheese.\" ~Dan Avidan','animal/cheese',NULL,NULL,126,4,NULL,112,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(256,'Flute','A hollow stick that turns breath into music. Or noise, depending on your skill level.','tool/instrument/flute',NULL,35,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(257,'Ceremonial Trident','A trident made of silver and gold? <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LmHk0n8FMVE\" target=\"_blank\">It must be ceremonial!</a>','tool/spear/trident-ceremonial',NULL,36,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,8,NULL,NULL,14,0,NULL,0,10),(258,'Ceremony of Shadows','On warm winter nights<br>\r\nshould dark clouds send<br>\r\na torrent of rain<br>\r\nand thunder,<br>\r\nthen<br>\r\nfrom dark, dripping palms<br>\r\nsome bald beasts come<br>\r\nwith scent of decay<br>\r\nand iron,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nrun.','tool/spear/trident-night',NULL,37,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,13,NULL,NULL,17,0,NULL,0,20),(259,'Ceremony of Fire',NULL,'tool/spear/trident-fire',NULL,38,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,2160,13,NULL,NULL,15,0,NULL,0,20),(260,'Ceremony of Sand and Sea','\"Building a boat isn\'t about weaving canvas, forging nails, or reading the sky. It\'s about giving a shared taste for the sea.\" ~Antoine de Saint Exupéry','tool/spear/trident-sand-and-sea','[[\"Summon the Sea!\", \"ceremonyOfSandAndSea/#\"]]',39,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,14,NULL,NULL,16,0,NULL,0,20),(261,'The Umbra','The pages seem to shift when you\'re not looking directly at them, and like most beginner\'s guides, it\'s remarkably unclear about several important things. Your pets seem to understand it just fine, though.','book/the-umbra','[[\"Read\", \"theUmbra/#/read\"]]',40,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(262,'Noodles','If you have noodley arms, don\'t worry about it: it just means your arms are _delicious_ when covered in tomato sauce - ooh, or maybe in a nice tonkatsu broth? Mmmm...\r\n\r\nSay, uh, you don\'t actually need _both_ your arms, do you?','bread/noodles',NULL,NULL,127,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(263,'3D Printer','With this, you\'ll be able to make neat items out of Plastic!\r\n\r\nWell, not _you_ you, but your pets, anyway.','tool/3d-printer',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(264,'Plastic Fishing Rod','Oh, it\'s even got the little leaves on it, and everything! Adorable.','tool/fishing-rod/plastic',NULL,41,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,3,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(265,'Small Plastic Bucket','A perfect bucket for holding liquids. Press <span style=\"color:red\">Ⓑ</span> to scoop or pour.\r\n\r\nEr, wait, sorry: wrong game.','tool/basket/plastic','[[\"Turn Upside-down\", \"reversable/#/flip\"]]',42,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(266,'Plastic Idol','Is it blasphemy or brilliance to 3D print a fertility goddess? The universe hasn\'t decided yet.','treasure/idol-plastic',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(267,'\"Gold\" Idol',NULL,'treasure/idol-quote-gold-unquote',NULL,43,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(268,'Magpie\'s Deal','Ha! Revenge!','treasure/magpie-deal','[[\"Get Quintessence\", \"magpieDeal/#/quint\"], [\"Get Bird Products\", \"magpieDeal/#/feathersAndEggs\"], [\"Get Five Sticks\", \"magpieDeal/#/sticks\"], [\"Get Shiny Metals\", \"magpieDeal/#/shinyMetals\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,9,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(269,'Box Box','Not an instance of reduplication, unfortunately. No: this box merely contains other boxes. Like how a juice box contains juice, and a pepperbox contains peppers.','box/cardboard','[[\"Open\", \"box/box/#/open\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(270,'Handicrafts Supply Box',NULL,'box/handicrafts','[[\"Open\", \"box/handicrafts/#/open\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(271,'Sandbox','The kind kids play in. Not the kind cats poop in.\n\nThat\'d be an unfortunate different kinds of thing to get mixed up.','box/sandbox','[[\"Raid\", \"box/sandbox/#/raid\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(272,'Pepperbox','I looked up Pepperbox on Wikipedia, and this is what they showed a picture of.\r\n\r\nI don\'t get it, either.','tool/gun/pepperbox','[[\"Disassemble\", \"box/pepperbox/#/disassemble\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(273,'Jukebox','\"A relic of rhythm and romance. A bastion of boogie-woogie.\"\n\nAgk, no! You have to read it, like, all _serious_-like!\n\nHere, try again; use a _serious_ voice this time, like-- like someone narrating an epic movie trailer! Like pretend it\'s Lord of the Rings, or something!\n\nOkay! Here it is again! (Remember to do the voice!)\n\n\"A relic of rhythm and romance. A bastion of boogie-woogie.\"\n\nHaa!\n\nYes! ? _Perfect._','box/jukebox','[[\"Listen\", \"box/jukebox/#/listen\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,1020,7,NULL,NULL,82,0,NULL,0,10),(274,'Red Yogurt',NULL,'yogurt/red',NULL,NULL,128,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(275,'Weird, Blue Egg','This egg is not for eating! It\'s on the verge of hatching!','animal/egg-enormous','[[\"Open?\", \"egg/weird-blue/#/hatch\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(276,'Grappling Hook','Let gravity be your guide, and momentum your muse, as you swing and sway in an aerial ballet of discovery!','tool/grappling-hook',NULL,44,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,5,126,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(277,'Glowing Four-sided Die','It\'s not just about the size; it\'s about how you use it.\r\n\r\nW-- no! That\'s not just a childish joke! It\'s true!\r\n\r\nHere, look: if a space you want to land on is... let\'s say 3 spaces away... would you rather roll a ten-sided die and have a 1-in-10 chance of landing on what you want? Or roll a four-sided and have a 1-in-4?\r\n\r\nSee? Childish joke and useful fact all _rolled_ into one!','die/d4','[[\"Roll\", \"die/#/roll\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(278,'Glowing Six-sided Die',NULL,'die/d6','[[\"Roll\", \"die/#/roll\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(279,'Glowing Eight-sided Die','If you\'ve never seen one of these before, don\'t worry: it\'s like a \"normal\" die, just a little bigger.','die/d8','[[\"Roll\", \"die/#/roll\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(280,'Box of Ores','Here, you can hold a piece of the world\'s heart in your hand, feel the weight of ages past, the silent whisper of time held within each stone...\n\n... and then an angry lobster pops out and starts snipping at you!\n\nBoxes just be like that sometimes, you know?','box/ores','[[\"Loot\", \"box/ores/#/loot\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(281,'XOR','Doubles as a very confusing paperweight.','resource/digital/xor',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,20,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(282,'Flower Basket',NULL,'box/basket-of-flowers','[[\"Raid\", \"basket/flower/#/loot\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,136,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(283,'Shiny Pail','This crystal-clear bucket is not only good for holding things in, but can be used as a magnifying glass. (Weird! Who would make such a thing?)','tool/basket/shiny','[[\"Turn Upside-down\", \"reversable/#/flip\"]]',45,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,3,NULL,NULL,58,0,NULL,0,1),(284,'Fiberglass Flute','Wait: it\'s made of fiberglass... and you put your lips on it. Is that _safe_?','tool/instrument/flute-fiberglass',NULL,46,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(285,'Bass Guitar','\"Why does this give +brawl?\" Have you ever _seen_ an anime?!','tool/instrument/guitar-bass',NULL,47,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(286,'Melodica','Imagine if a harmonica and a piano had a baby. And the baby oozed music. Instead of... whatever it is babies are usually oozing.','tool/instrument/melodica',NULL,48,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,6,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(287,'Maraca','\\*Tshka-tshka!\\*','tool/instrument/maraca','[[\"Take Apart\", \"maraca/#/takeApart\"]]',49,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(288,'NUL','Question #22: Can you hold nothing?','resource/digital/null',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(289,'Password','<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7U-RbOKanYs\" target=\"_blank\">It better not be \"password1\", or even \"correct horse battery staple\"!</a>','resource/digital/password','[[\"Erase\", \"password/#/erase\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(290,'Cryptocurrency Wallet',NULL,'resource/digital/wallet','[[\"Raid\", \"cryptocurrencyWallet/#/unlock\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(291,'Renaming Scroll','\"There are only two hard things in Computer Science: cache invalidation and naming things.\" ~Phil Karlton\r\n\r\nI\'ll leave it to you to decide how well that quote applies to the profession of pet care...','scroll/renaming','[[\"Rename a Pet\", \"renamingScroll\", \"page\"], [\"Rename a Spirit Companion\", \"renameSpiritCompanion\", \"page\"], [\"Rename Yourself\", \"renameYourself\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,20),(292,'Benjamin Franklin','\"Die Thiere spielen nicht, weil sie jung sind, sondern sie haben eine Jugend, weil sie spielen müssen.\" ~not Benjamin Franklin','tool/benjamin-franklin','[[\"Fly\", \"benjaminFranklin/#/fly\"]]',50,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,8,NULL,NULL,70,0,NULL,0,10),(293,'Fish Stew','The secret is to use Mirepoix.','soup/fish',NULL,NULL,129,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(294,'Spicy Fish Stew','The chunky Tomato almost makes it a sort of fish chili.','soup/fish-spicy',NULL,NULL,130,8,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(295,'Apricobbler',NULL,'cobbler/apricot',NULL,NULL,131,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(296,'Berry Cobbler','It\'s like berries were having a rave in an oven, and dough was invited, too.\n\n... you always host the _weirdest_ parties.','cobbler/berry',NULL,NULL,132,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(297,'Red Cobbler',NULL,'cobbler/red',NULL,NULL,133,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(298,'Cobbler Recipe','The dessert kind, not the shoe kind. (It\'d be weird to call the shoe kind a \"recipe.\")','note/recipe','[[\"Read\", \"note/cobblers/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"note/cobblers/#/upload\"], [\"Erase\", \"note/#/erase\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,60,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(299,'Popcorn',NULL,'veggie/corn-popped',NULL,NULL,134,10,NULL,NULL,30,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(300,'Buttered Popcorn','If popcorn had a dating profile, \"Buttered\" would be its most swiped-right pic.','veggie/corn-popped-buttered',NULL,NULL,135,14,NULL,NULL,45,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(301,'Useless Fizz','At least it was fun to make!','ambiguous/useless-fizz',NULL,NULL,NULL,4,NULL,121,15,0,3,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(302,'Onigiri','The recipe is about as simple as it gets!','onigiri/plain',NULL,NULL,136,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(303,'Fried Egg','Did you know that the yolk of a fried egg is actually a natural stress reliever? That\'s right - just the act of breaking open a fried egg and allowing the yolk to ooze out has been shown to reduce anxiety and promote a sense of calm and well-being!\r\n\r\nNeat!','animal/egg-fried',NULL,NULL,137,6,NULL,123,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(304,'Sour Cream','A marvel of culinary alchemy, where milk meets bacteria to create a tangy delight!\n\nIt can also be used as a soothing face mask! Just make sure to separate your face cream from your nacho cream...\n\n... or don\'t! Whatever! I\'m not your _mom!_','animal/sour-cream',NULL,NULL,138,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(305,'Fish Stroganoff','Necessity is the mother of invention; the distinct lack of beef on the island is the mother of Fish Stroganoff.','pasta/stroganoff',NULL,NULL,139,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(306,'Fish Shroomanoff',NULL,'pasta/shroomanoff',NULL,NULL,140,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(307,'Stroganoff Recipe',NULL,'note/recipe','[[\"Read\", \"note/stroganoff/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"note/stroganoff/#/upload\"], [\"Erase\", \"note/#/erase\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,60,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(308,'Mini Melowatern Onigiri',NULL,'onigiri/melowatern',NULL,NULL,141,8,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(309,'Fermented Fish Onigiri','Sometimes love takes time, you know?','onigiri/fish-fermented',NULL,NULL,142,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(310,'Fish Onigiri',NULL,'onigiri/fish',NULL,NULL,143,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(311,'Tentacle Onigiri','It\'s items like this - items that are almost picture-perfect replicas of their real-life counterparts - that really make me appreciate the art talent behind Poppy Seed Pets, you know?','onigiri/tentacle',NULL,NULL,144,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(312,'Flour Tortilla',NULL,'bread/tortilla-flour',NULL,NULL,145,3,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(313,'Cheese Quesadilla',NULL,'sandwich/quesadilla-cheese',NULL,NULL,146,12,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(314,'Grilled Cheese',NULL,'sandwich/grilled-cheese',NULL,NULL,147,13,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(315,'Chocolate Ice Cream',NULL,'ice-cream/chocolate',NULL,NULL,148,11,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(316,'Blueberry Ice Cream','Is there such a thing as Blueberry Ice Cream, irl? I feel like I\'ve never seen any, before. Why is that? We can have Blue _Bell_ ice cream, and Blue _Bunny_ ice cream, but no Blue<em>berry</em> Ice Cream???\n\nI hate this timeline.','ice-cream/blueberry',NULL,NULL,149,11,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(317,'Blackberry Ice Cream',NULL,'ice-cream/blackberry',NULL,NULL,150,11,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(318,'Naner Ice Cream',NULL,'ice-cream/naner',NULL,NULL,151,12,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(319,'Honeydont Ice Cream',NULL,'ice-cream/honeydont',NULL,NULL,152,12,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(320,'SOUP',NULL,'book/SOUP','[[\"READ\", \"SOUP/#/READ\"], [\"SHOW TO COOKING BUDDY\", \"SOUP/#/UPLOAD\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(321,'Tomato Soup',NULL,'soup/tomato',NULL,NULL,153,8,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(322,'Money Sink','Neither subtle, nor original...','furniture/money-sink',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,15,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(323,'\"Chicken\" Noodle Soup','Every attempt to summon chickens on the island has just resulted in more fish. Summoning turkey works fine though, oddly enough.','soup/chicken-noodle',NULL,NULL,154,11,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(324,'Soy Sauce',NULL,'ingredient/soy-sauce',NULL,NULL,NULL,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(325,'Chocolate Bar','In Poppy Seed Pets, all you gotta\' do is combine Cocoa Beans and Sugar. In real life, <a href=\"https://www.instructables.com/id/From-Bean-to-Bar-Dark-Chocolate-from-Scratch/\" target=\"_blank\">it\'s a whole, dang thing!</a> <a href=\"https://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/how-to-temper-chocolate-356869\" target=\"_blank\">And then some!</a>','candy/chocolate/bar',NULL,NULL,155,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(326,'Spicy Chocolate Bar','Life\'s about trying new things, you know?\n\nUnless the thing is a Bacon-maple Chocolate Bar. F**k _that_ s**t. That\'s, like, the number one reason maple\'s not in the game!\n\nNah, that\'s not true. I\'m just sayin\' stuff for the sake of a silly poppyopedia entry. Bacon-maple chocolate, surprisingly, is almost good enough to put in your mouth. I\'d put it in the game.','candy/chocolate/bar-spicy',NULL,NULL,156,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(327,'Orange Chocolate Bar',NULL,'candy/chocolate/bar-orange',NULL,NULL,157,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(328,'Unicorn Horn','For being a Halloween costume, it seems awfully... sparkly.\r\n\r\nYou don\'t think--...\r\n\r\nNo.\r\n\r\nNo, it couldn\'t be.\r\n\r\nI\'m sure it\'s just a regular Halloween costume.','hat/horn-unicorn',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,1,0,2,19,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,25),(329,'Behatting Scroll','In addition to being a hat, reading this scroll to a pet will allow that pet to wear hats! Unfortunately, doing so also consumes the scroll, so if you want your pet to wear this scroll as a hat, you\'ll need at least two of them!','scroll/behatting','[[\"Read\", \"behattingScroll\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,197,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,25),(330,'Tinfoil Hat','I once wore a Tinfoil Hat to a party. Not for the alien protection, but because it matched my shoes. Little did I know, it not only blocked extraterrestrial eavesdroppers, but also dodged all the gossip. Now, if I can just find shoes that repel unsolicited advice...','hat/foil',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,2,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(331,'Upside-down Plastic Bucket','Well now what? You can\'t store anything - certainly not liquids - in a bucket like this!\r\n\r\nMaybe it could be worn as a hat?','hat/bucket-plastic','[[\"Turn Rightside-up\", \"reversable/#/flip\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,3,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(332,'Witch\'s Hat','Does a witch\'s hat make a witch, or does a witch make a witch\'s hat? Or maybe a pointy hat is just a pointy hat.','hat/witch',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,4,0,6,NULL,NULL,69,0,NULL,0,15),(333,'House Fairy',NULL,'animal/fairy','[[\"Say Hello\", \"fairy/#/hello\"], [\"Build a Fireplace\", \"fairy/#/buildFireplace\"], [\"Ask about Quintessence\", \"fairy/#/quintessence\"], [\"Make Fairy Floss\", \"fairy/#/makeFairyFloss\"]]',53,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(334,'Fairy Ring',NULL,'ring/fairy','[[\"Pull the Wings off\", \"fairyRing/#/takeApart\"]]',51,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,5,NULL,NULL,19,0,NULL,0,10),(335,'Burnt Log','There\'s a curious spark of magic in this burnt log...\r\n\r\nI know you can\'t tell, because you\'re just looking at it over the internet, but take my word for it: curious spark!','plant/log-burnt','[[\"Break Apart\", \"burntLog/#/break\"]]',NULL,NULL,32,NULL,NULL,0,0,25,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(336,'Poker','These things are pretty mean-lookin\' right? Like, I look at these and think \"are you sure this tool was designed for poking fires, and not humans? \'Cause damn.\"','tool/poker',NULL,52,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(337,'Ant Queen','This is what happens when you feed ants! (10% of the time! (Just like in real life!))','bug/ant-queen','[[\"Squish\", \"bug/#/squish\"], [\"Put Outside\", \"bug/#/putOutside\"], [\"Feed\", \"feedBug\", \"page\"], [\"Introduce Yourself\", \"bug/#/talkToQueen\", \"story\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,106,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,5),(338,'l33t h4xx0r','Can you jam with the console cowboys in cyberspace?','tool/sword/l33th4xx0r',NULL,54,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,11,NULL,NULL,37,0,NULL,0,20),(339,'Spirit Polymorph Potion','Are we meant to read the name as \"a potion which polymorphs spirits\", or as \"a polymorph potion, which is itself a spirit\"? You know what I mean? It\'s, like, ambiguous.','potion/spirit-polymorph','[[\"Give to Pet\", \"spiritPolymorphPotion\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(340,'Iridescent Hand Cannon','Don\'t worry: it has a 90% chance of not literally blowing up in your face! Those are really good odds!!!','t