,10),(719,'Sweet Roll','Not to be confused for sweetbread.','dessert/sweet-roll',NULL,NULL,285,10,NULL,157,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(720,'Red Balloon',NULL,'tool/balloon/red',NULL,150,NULL,0,NULL,26,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(721,'Orange Balloon','If you poke a hole in a balloon (or just untie the string and let the air escape) and then streeetch the balloon out, you\'d have a big ol\' flat sheet of rubber. A flat sheet of rubber doesn\'t have any holes in it, though! So... if adding _one_ hole to a balloon makes a shape with _zero_ holes in it... does that mean a balloon has _-1 holes???_\r\n\r\nMath is weird.','tool/balloon/orange',NULL,151,NULL,0,NULL,27,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(722,'Yellow Balloon',NULL,'tool/balloon/yellow',NULL,152,NULL,0,NULL,28,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(723,'Green Balloon',NULL,'tool/balloon/green',NULL,153,NULL,0,NULL,29,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(724,'Blue Balloon',NULL,'tool/balloon/blue',NULL,154,NULL,0,NULL,30,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(725,'Purple Balloon','Or, if you prefer, _violet_.','tool/balloon/purple',NULL,155,NULL,0,NULL,31,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(726,'World\'s Second-best Sugar Cookie','Honestly, it seems to taste about the same as the World\'s _actually_-Best Sugar Cookie, just a little crunchier. Maybe some Baking Powder would help it rise more?','dessert/cookie-sugar-second-best',NULL,NULL,286,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(727,'Pan-fried Tofu',NULL,'plant/bean-cheese-fried',NULL,NULL,287,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(728,'The Art of Tofu','\"I also make really good tofu.\" ~ Sun Tzu, <cite>The Art of War</cite>','book/art-of-tofu','[[\"Read\", \"artOfTofu/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"artOfTofu/#/upload\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,120,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(729,'Everlasting Syllabub','I know what you\'re thinking. \"Syllabub that can last forever? Nonsense! Never mind the orange rind, the wine on its own is more than enough to curdle the 