4,'Twu Wuv','A physical manifestation of your pet\'s love - er, I mean, _wuv_ - for you.\n\nI\'m sure you don\'t need _me_ telling you how wuv works, but just in case you were out sick that day in your 6th grade health class: you should keep it around the house, so your pets can craft something out of it. Like, you know, a rad bow, or something.','resource/twu-wuv',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(935,'Wed Bawwoon',NULL,'tool/balloon/wed',NULL,280,NULL,0,NULL,80,0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(936,'Pink Bow',NULL,'hat/bow-pink',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,81,45,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,35),(937,'Fierierstone','It used to be believed that a Fierierstone could keep a family warm for an entire winter, but modern science tells us that it\'s only capable of keeping a Fireplace going for about 18 hours.\r\n\r\nIt also used to be believed that \"fierier\" wasn\'t a word, but modern internet dictionaries tell us that it _totally_ is.\r\n\r\nThe modern world is a surprisingly informative place, if not a slightly chillier and more full-of-weird-word-choices-ier one.','mineral/firierstone',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,1080,0,57,NULL,83,0,NULL,0,1),(938,'Worms','Why would you put these on your head?\r\n\r\n_Why?_','animal/worms',NULL,NULL,344,10,NULL,82,0,0,58,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(939,'Gummy Worms','I mean, you put _real_ Worms on your head; you clearly won\'t be stopped from doing the same with the _gummy_ ones.','candy/gummy/worms',NULL,NULL,345,5,NULL,83,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(940,'Wormhole','Or as I like to call it, a \"wrigglemaw\".','space/wormhole',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,2,59,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(941,'Mushroom Broccoli Krahi','Most people would say this is made of five vegetables, but not you and I! We\'re more pedantic than that! We know it\'s made of two vegetables, two fruits, and a fungus!\r\n\r\nAgk, dangit, I forgot about the Ginger! Ugh, the whole description is _ruined_ now!','veggie/mushroom-broccoli-krahi',NULL,NULL,346,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(942,'White Épée','A strange weapon apparently blessed by either the spirits of birds, or of pegasi.\r\n\r\nIt\'s, uh-- it\'s easy to get the two confused.','tool/sword/epee-white',NULL,284,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,7,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(943,'Livewire',NULL,'tool/livewire',NULL,285,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(944,'Blue Bow',NULL,'hat/bow-blue',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,84,45,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,35),(945,'Chocolate Key','In some senses it\'s logical to assume that a Chocolate Key would open a Chocolate Chest, but think about it: a key made of chocolate would break the moment you tried to turn it!\r\n\r\nNo, this key must have some _other_ purpose...','key/chocolate',NULL,286,347,5,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(947,'Chocolate Top Hat','This extravagant hat is not suited for the timorous, or abstemious.','hat/top-hat-chocolate',NULL,NULL,348,10,NULL,85,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,15),(948,'Chocolate-stained Cloth',NULL,'cloth/chocolate-stained',NULL,NULL,NULL,5,NULL,NULL,45,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(949,'Chocolate Wine',NULL,'wine/chocolate',NULL,NULL,349,5,NULL,NULL,15,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(950,'Scroll of Chocolate','This scroll is written in esoteric - and highly-goopy - chocolatese, and is therefore both impossible to read, and impossible to resist licking. Maybe if you just, like, stick it to one of your pets\' tools, some of the scroll\'s magic will manage to seep in? \\*shrugs\\* Couldn\'t hurt to try!','scroll/chocolate',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,420,3,60,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,5),(951,'Le Chocolat','The preeminent book on all things chocolate, written by an author who has, to this day, remained _deliciously_ anonymous.','book/le-chocolat','[[\"Read\", \"leChocolat/#/read\"], [\"Show to Cooking Buddy\", \"leChocolat/#/upload\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,60,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(952,'Chocolate Syrup','\"Maybe if I pour this Chocolate Syrup on a chest, I\'ll get a Chocolate Chest,\" you\'re thinking, but that\'s not how Poppy Seed Pets works. Remember, Chocolate Syrup is a \"spice\", and you can only combine spices with foods.','ingredient/chocolate-syrup',NULL,NULL,NULL,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,22,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(953,'Chocolate Cue Ball','I know what you\'re thinking about the graphic. You took one look at it, and were like \"look, I\'ve played a lot of pet games, but Poppy Seed Pets\' standards for graphics are just... wow... incredible! I feel _transported_ looking at this! The artist has really captured the essence of their subject in a way that no one else could!\" And I\'m humbled; I truly am. Thank you.','candy/chocolate/cue-ball',NULL,NULL,351,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(954,'Chocolate Chest',NULL,'box/chocolate-chest','[[\"Loot\", \"box/chocolate/#/open\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,5),(955,'Chocolate Feather Bonnet','If there\'s a bee in this bonnet, it\'s made of chocolate, too.','hat/chocolate-feather-bonnet',NULL,NULL,352,10,NULL,86,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,15),(956,'Mooncake',NULL,'cake/moon',NULL,NULL,353,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(957,'Photon','It\'s massless, but still somehow takes up space in your house.\r\n\r\nHuh.','space/photon',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(958,'Avocado','When I think \"fruit\", I don\'t usually think \"fatty and creamy\", yet here we are...','fruit/avocado',NULL,NULL,354,6,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(959,'Chocolate Lava Cake','You\'d make a bigger mess of yourself eating this than that time you mistook a tiny, sleeping Amalgam for a Naner Puddin\'.\r\n\r\nAnd this is why we leave the eating to the pets in Poppy Seed Pets, and not to the humans.','cake/chocolate-lava',NULL,NULL,355,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(960,'Chocolate Lava-lava Cake','I mean... what did you _think_ was gonna happen?','cake/chocolate-lava-lava',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,200,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(961,'Twiggen Berries',NULL,'tool/wand/berry',NULL,289,NULL,20,NULL,NULL,570,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(962,'Carotene Stick','The carrot part lures the fish in; the stick part smacks the stuffing out of them.\r\n\r\nIt\'s hard being a fish.','tool/fishing-rod/carrot',NULL,290,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,360,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(963,'Mericarp','It\'s a plant thing; not a fish thing.','tool/wand/mericarp',NULL,291,NULL,9,NULL,NULL,660,7,61,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(964,'Whisk','Did you know that the world\'s largest whisk is actually located on the moon? That\'s right - in the early days of space exploration, astronauts placed a massive whisk on the moon\'s surface as a symbol of humanity\'s culinary accomplishments. The whisk is reportedly over 100 feet long and is visible from Earth with a powerful telescope. Some conspiracy theorists even believe that the whisk is still in use, with extraterrestrial beings using it to whip up delicious lunar treats!\r\n\r\nNeat!','tool/whisk/whisk',NULL,293,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(965,'Culinary Knife','Well. That\'s _one_ interpretation, anyway.','tool/whisk/dagger',NULL,294,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(966,'No Whisk, No Reward','But it does have the Whisk. So you will get the reward. That\'s how it works; that\'s what it means.','tool/whisk/no-whisk-no-reward',NULL,295,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,10,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,20),(967,'Snickerblade','It laughs, _and_ it\'s a vorpal weapon.\r\n\r\nSomeone was having a laugh, themselves, when they made this. I just hope they didn\'t lose any limbs in the process.','tool/sword/snickerblade',NULL,296,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,16,62,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,30),(968,'Butterknife',NULL,'tool/sword/butter','[[\"Mold into Butter\", \"butterknife/#/mold\"]]',298,NULL,4,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,23,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(969,'Wunderbuss','This strange and powerful contraption is capable of producing whatever item its holder wishes. There are, however, some caveats...','tool/gun/wund