te! If you value your Chocolate Feather Bonnet, I wouldn\'t get it too close to one of these - certainly don\'t let the two touch!','tool/wand/etalocohc',NULL,490,516,10,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1431,'Non-chocolate Feather Bonnet',NULL,'hat/red-feather-bonnet',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,277,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,15),(1432,'De-chocolated Meringue','At last: your lifelong quest to discover what\'s left of a Chocolate Meringue after magically evicting all the chocolate has come to an end.','dessert/blue-meringue',NULL,NULL,517,6,NULL,278,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1433,'Thaumatoxic Cookies','These cookies radiate dangerous levels of pure, magical energy. They definitely should NOT be eaten, but perhaps your pets can find some other use for them...','dessert/cookies-thaumatoxic',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1434,'Odd Little Hammer','Holding this hammer, you catch a faint whiff of chocolate.\r\n\r\nOdd.','tool/hammer/odd-little',NULL,491,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1435,'Strawberry-covered Naner','Strawberries? In Poppy Seed Pets? Most unusual! Some crazy-powerful magic must have been involved in the creation of this item...','dessert/naner-strawberry-covered',NULL,492,518,20,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1436,'Mildly Thaumatoxic Top Hat','It\'s only _mildly_ thaumatoxic!\r\n\r\n<small>_This hat is known to the State of California to cause reproductive harm._</small>','hat/top-hat-thaumatoxic',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,279,720,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,15),(1437,'Headsnake',NULL,'hat/snake',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,281,30,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1438,'Wicked Broom',NULL,'tool/broom/wicked',NULL,494,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,690,15,147,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,30),(1439,'Woher Cuán Nani-nani','Eh? Why?','tool/axe/woher-cuan-nani-nani',NULL,496,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,4,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1440,'Carrot Wine',NULL,'wine/carrot','[]',NULL,519,0,NULL,NULL,15,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1441,'Carrot Win