,0,NULL,NULL,560,10,150,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1453,'Snailppling Hook','The name doesn\'t roll off the tongue, but at least the spiral theming is strong?','tool/grappling-hook-snail',NULL,504,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,7,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1454,'Geodesic Curlicue','\"Putting all reason aside, you exchange / What you got for a thing that\'s hypnotic and strange.\" ~They Might Be Giants','tool/crystal-ball/geodesic-curlicue',NULL,505,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,4,151,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1455,'Zawinski\'s Law','\"Every program attempts to expand until it can read mail. Those programs which cannot so expand are replaced by ones which can.\" ~Zawinski','tool/sword/zawinskis-law',NULL,507,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1456,'Missing Mail',NULL,'trinket/letter','[[\"Read\", \"missingMail/#/read\"]]',NULL,NULL,4,NULL,NULL,60,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1457,'Plastic Bottle','Plastic?!? What\'s wrong with Glass??? \\*sigh\\*','box/bottle','[[\"Open\", \"plasticBottle/#/open\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,290,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1458,'Traffic Light',NULL,'tool/traffic-light',NULL,508,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1459,'Traffic Cone',NULL,'hat/traffic-cone',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,291,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1460,'Imperturbable Toucan','What are those, um, British guards, or whatever, with the hats? Where you can, like, dance around and shit and they won\'t even care? I guess? (Is that just a movie thing?)\n\nAnyway, this toucan is like that. But definitely for real - not just in a movie.','hat/toucan','[[\"Go! Be free!\", \"toucan/#/setFree\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,292,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,5),(1461,'Jelly-filled Donut',NULL,'bread/donut-jelly-filled','[[\"Scoop Out Jelly\", \"jellyDonut/#/empty\"]]',NULL,522,25,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1462,'Aos Sí',NULL,'tool/wand/aos-si',NULL,509,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,7,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1463,'Bean Sídhe','If you think this item has anything to do with Beans, who-oa nellie! You\'ve got another thing comin\', let me tell you!','tool/wand/banshee',NULL,510,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,10,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1464,'Merchant\'s Other Cap','The first one wasn\'t good enough, I guess??\n\nC\'mon, merchants - why y\'all gotta\' be so picky?','hat/merchants-2',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,293,105,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1465,'Less-heavy Heavy Hammer','It flies with the grace of an ill-shapen boulder, but hey: it didn\'t fly _at all_ before!','tool/hammer/heavy-light',NULL,511,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,11,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,15),(1466,'Way Too Much Lightning','Is this safe to hold? Like, I get it\'s not safe to _eat_, but can I at least _hold_ it? And, uh, if so: can I hold it in my mouth? I\'M ASKING FOR A FRIEND!','tool/spear/too-much-lightning',NULL,512,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,13,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,10),(1467,'Mortar or Pestle','There are some things science still hasn\'t answered. And I\'m not talking about \"why is there something instead of nothing?\" - that one\'s basically sorted - no, I\'m talking about \"which bit is the \'mortar\' and which bit is the \'pestle\'?\" There are literally _none_ who know!','tool/mortar-or-pestle',NULL,513,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1468,'Licorice Gooplin','Some people say Gooplins smell like licorice? Apparently that\'s the origin for this candy, anyway. I don\'t think _my_ Gooplin smells like that, but my Gooplin also has Black Hole Tum, so mostly he just smells like... _Dark Matter_...','candy/gummy/licorice-gooplin',NULL,NULL,524,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1469,'Apricrate',NULL,'box/apricrate','[[\"Raid\", \"apricrate/#/open\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,294,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,5),(1470,'Empty Crate',NULL,'box/empty-crate',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,295,0,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1471,'Aprihat','All natural! Made from real Apricots!','hat/aprihat',NULL,NULL,525,6,15,296,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,2),(1472,'Gold and Apricots',NULL,'tool/wand/gold-and-apricots',NULL,515,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,0,153,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1473,'Apricot Coffee Bean Tea with Mammal Extract','\"I have a great idea,\" said the marketing department, \"let\'s capitalize on a local festival by creating a _festive drink!_\" This, apparently, is what they came up with.','tea/apricot-festival',NULL,NULL,526,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1474,'Tile: Pluot Parade',NULL,'tile/pluot-parade',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,30,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,90,0,1),(1475,'Olives',NULL,'fruit/olives',NULL,NULL,527,5,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1476,'Gulab Jamun','The tricky part is simmering the milk down into solids, but once that\'s done you mix it up with some wheat flour and butter, fry it up, and soak it in sugar syrup! Bam - done!','dessert/gulab-jamun',NULL,NULL,523,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1477,'Syrniki',NULL,'bread/syrniki',NULL,NULL,529,12,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1478,'Unstuffed Draniki','It\'s not that this Draniki was once stuffed, and someone _cruely_ removed the stuffing from it - it\'s much worse than that: this Draniki was never stuffed to begin with!','veggie/draniki',NULL,NULL,530,7,NULL,297,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1479,'Spaghet Jaffle',NULL,'sandwich/spaghet',NULL,NULL,531,11,NULL,298,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1480,'PB&P','PB... and _pickles?!_\n\nWeird.','sandwich/pbp',NULL,NULL,532,9,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1481,'Chip Butty','_Chip_ Butty? I get the butter part, but those are _clearly_ frites, or at least fries!','sandwich/chip-butty',NULL,NULL,533,7,NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1482,'Sandwill Scroch','Making your own Sandwich Scr-- er, I mean, Sandwill Scroch is easy!\n\n1. Get a nice piece of paper, and cut it two\n2. Butter each half on one side\n3. Nut-butter each half on the side you didn\'t regular-type butter\n4. Get a fish (dead is easier, but you do you)\n5. Put the nut-buttered side of each paper half against the fish\n6. Fry with a bit of Quintessence, flipping occasionally, until golden-brown and delicious\n\nYour Sandwill Scroch is now reedy to red-- er, I mean, reddy to reed!','scroll/sandwich','[[\"Read\", \"scroll/sandwich/#/read\"]]',NULL,534,37,NULL,NULL,420,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1483,'Forge Blueprint','With nothing more than a piece of Iron and a Heavy Hammer, it\'s apparently possible to build a fully-functioning, HEAT-channeling Forge. Why, with such incredible HEAT, you could probably make and melt all kinds of things...','note/blueprint-forge','[[\"Read\", \"forgeBlueprint\", \"page\"]]',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,90,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1484,'Clay Brick','A brick is a versatile thing! Why, you can even wear it as a hat! How many things can you say _that_ about in Poppy Seed Pets?\n\nHuh? What? You can wear Gummy Worms and bottles of Ponzu as hats?!?!\n\nWell... ... ... fine. I guess bricks aren\'t so special after all! I HOPE YOU\'RE HAPPY! \\*flees, crying\\*','mineral/brick','[[\"Add to Fireplace\", \"brick/#/addToFireplace\"]]',518,NULL,0,NULL,299,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1485,'Rapscallion',NULL,'tool/sword/rapscallion',NULL,519,NULL,70,NULL,NULL,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1),(1486,'Fancy Teapot','Some people have wondered if there\'s a teapot, too small to be seen by telescopes, orbiting the Sun somewhere in space between the Earth and Mars. Others have wondered if there\'s an optimal number of teapots to have in a room.\n\nIt seems teapots are the source of many questions, both philosophical and practical.','tool/teapot','[[\"Smash\", \"fancyTeapot/#/smash\"]]',520,NULL,0,NULL,300,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,1);
