INSERT INTO `story_section` VALUES (1,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh! A human! Hello? Can you hear me?','[{\"text\": \"Yes! Can you hear me?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 3, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"No.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 2, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(2,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Ah. Definitely a human...','[{\"text\": \"Sorry. My name is %user.name%. Who are you?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 4, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(3,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh! I can! How wonderfully unexpected!','[{\"text\": \"My name is %user.name%. Who are you?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 4, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(4,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','My name is Sharuminyinka. But I\'m sure you haven\'t heard of me before. I\'m the Goddess of all On. Well... used to be. There isn\'t any On left anymore.','[{\"text\": \"What is... \'On\'?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 5, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(5,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','That\'s the problem... no one knows, anymore. Everything about On has been erased from creation. My brother and I were the only ones who remembered it, but we forgot millennia ago...','[{\"text\": \"You don\'t remember _anything_?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 7, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Millennia ago?! How long have you lived?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 6, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(6,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','We\'ve been around since almost the beginning. Certainly long before this universe was born.','[{\"text\": \"What do you remember?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 7, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"You mentioned a brother?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 9, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"How old is... everything?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 17, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(7,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Not much. Hm... beauty. Love. Purpose. But it\'s possible that I\'m only remembering my own feelings, and not On itself. Even the God of Writhing Tentacles probably has these feelings about his domain...','[{\"text\": \"Th-- the God of Writhing Tentacles?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 8, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"You mentioned a brother?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 9, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(8,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh, no, I just made that up as an example. There\'s no god like that. Hm. Well, not that I\'m aware of, anyway. I guess there could be...','[{\"text\": \"Uh, anyway: you mentioned a brother?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 9, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(9,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Yes, Tig, my younger brother. Well, only technically: we\'re twins. But I was born first. He always liked to remind me of that... but he\'s been unwell recently. Ever since On was erased from creation, he\'s been depressed.\r\n\r\nHe tried becoming the God of Orange Tree Leaves for a while, but he got into a nasty relationship with an Angel of Orange Seeds, and the God of Trees eventually banished him. Even the Goddess of Plants got involved. It was... embarrassing, I suppose, is the only word for it.\r\n\r\nAh, but that was all nearly four millennia ago. Ever since then he\'s just... I don\'t know. Slept. Wandered. I think he\'s trying to be forgotten. Well: I\'m sure he is.','[{\"text\": \"His name is \'_Tig_\'?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 10, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"A... \'nasty\' relationship?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 12, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"If your brother is forgotten, will he also...?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 13, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(10,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Yes. Why?','[{\"text\": \"And your name is \'Sharuminyinka\'.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 11, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(11,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Hm. I\'m not sure I understand what you\'re getting at, %user.name%, but before choosing whether or not to vocalize your potentially-disrespectful line of thought, I would like to remind you that even if I am a _lost_ goddess, I am still _a goddess_ - a creature infinitely more powerful than any mortal.','[{\"text\": \"Oh, uh, no, I didn\'t have any more questions. About that. Um. So, your brother... you said he\'s trying to be forgotten?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 13, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(12,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Ugh. It really isn\'t worth recounting. Although I definitely wouldn\'t eat any orange seeds, if I were you.','[{\"text\": \"Huh. Well... is your brother doing okay?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 13, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(13,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','The universe exists the way it does, because people believe that it does. There are stars because there are many that believe there are stars. There are gods and fairies because there are many that believe _they_ exist. By that same token, there is no more On, because no one remembers it. And, as you have guessed, if no one remembers Tig, then he, too, shall stop existing.','[{\"text\": \"What about you? Why don\'t you remember the On? And won\'t you always remember your brother?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 14, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(14,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Ah. Well, you know why gods usually come in pairs...','[{\"text\": \"They do?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 15, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"I didn\'t know that...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 15, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(15,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','In case one should fall asleep... or perhaps become intoxicated... and forget, even if just for a moment... even the most important thing in all creation... lost forever because the only two who still remembered it could not control their own grief...','[{\"text\": \"Oh :| Sorry...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 16, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(16,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Well. It was all millennia ago. Haha. How silly of me. But I suppose it makes me think of my little brother. Or of me. Though somehow I worry less about myself.\r\n\r\nSorry. Goodness. Talking to a mortal like this. I suppose it\'s just been so long.','[{\"text\": \"Why not talk to other gods?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 18, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Is there anything I can do to help?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 20, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(17,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Haha. Another question that doesn\'t have an answer, unfortunately. The God of All died long ago, and with it, the last memory of what there was before. But that\'s... another thing entirely.','[{\"text\": \"Huh. So do you remember _anything_ about On?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 18, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Huh. Oh yeah: you mentioned a brother earlier?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 9, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(18,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','First we lost our reason for being, then the whole thing with the orange trees... believe me, other gods know our situation well. More than I\'d like.','[{\"text\": \"Oh. Well at least you won\'t be forgotten, then?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 19, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(19,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','I told you: things exist because people believe they do. If my brother and I are remembered only for our misdeeds, then that\'s all of us that will remain. I\'ll become nothing more than a lost goddess, and he, just a troublemaker and outcast.\r\n\r\nIn a way, you could say that that\'s already what we are... but I don\'t want my last moments to be someone\'s fading memory of what a failed and broken goddess is. I understand why my brother wishes to just be forgotten altogether, but I\'m not willing to give up so easily!\r\n\r\nI\'ll save us both. I am the older sister, after all.','[{\"text\": \"Is there anything I can do to help?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 20, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(20,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Remember me! Us! As God and Goddess of all On!','[{\"text\": \"O-- okay. I mean... is it that easy?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 21, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(21,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Well, it\'d help to have a few things around to remind you, and tell others, as well. Things to keep the story going. Nothing as big as a temple or shrine - I couldn\'t ask that much - but... oh, how do humans like to communicate these days? I feel like you used to do more tapestries, then I looked away for a bit, and you were all talking into these phones, but that\'s not the same at all...','[{\"text\": \"Er... well we have the Internet.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 22, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(22,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Hm. It certainly sounds like a tool for connecting. Or perhaps for binding? (I should see if I can meet its gods or goddesses.) Well: I\'ll leave the Internet part to you.\r\n\r\nBut I couldn\'t possibly ask you to do something without giving you something in return! Equivalent exchange is the way of creation, after all. Oh, wait, no, I know this: \'Conservation of Energy\', right?','[{\"text\": \"That\'s from physics. \'Energy cannot be created or destroyed.\'\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 23, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(23,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','It\'s close enough. I\'m sure someone will broaden the scope a bit more, eventually. Someone always does.','[{\"text\": \"...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 24, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"So what\'s the exchange you want to make?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 24, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(24,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Ah! The exchange! Right!\r\n\r\nIf I give you something that will help continue the memory of my brother and I, will you use it?','[{\"text\": \"That\'s a little vague, but...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 25, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Sure!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 26, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(25,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh, you\'re right, that probably does sound a bit ominous...','[{\"text\": \"...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 26, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(26,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','It\'s a wand that will let you and your little aliens create objects in our honor. Then all you have to do is Internet them! If you can bring me... let\'s see... an iron staff... some feathers... a spider... I\'ll make the wand for you. Or a quintessence and the spider, if you can\'t find the other stuff.','[{\"text\": \"\'Little aliens\'?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 27, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"An \'iron staff\'? Will a Poker do?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 30, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Alright! I\'ll go get that stuff for you!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 32, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(27,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','The ones you keep in your house? I\'m fairly certain that\'s the right word. \'Aliens\' are creatures from another planet, right?','[{\"text\": \"That\'s the right word, but...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 28, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(28,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','I\'ve seen them coming across the thread that connects your planet to the other. You didn\'t know?','[{\"text\": \"Oh, the Portal? I guess I didn\'t think about it?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 29, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(29,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Goodness! I-- well. Never mind.','[{\"text\": \"...?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 31, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(30,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Ah, yes-yes! That would be perfect.','[{\"text\": \"Um, but also: did you say \'little aliens\'?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 27, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Poker. Feathers. Spider. Got it.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 32, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(31,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Anyway! Iron staff. Feathers. Spider. Sound good?','[{\"text\": \"Sure!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 32, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(32,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Thank you so much! I really mean it. I don\'t know how it will all play out in the end - the Goddesses of Time certainly won\'t tell anyone - but it really means a lot that someone would try.\r\n\r\nAnd I think you\'ll find the wand fun!','[{\"text\": \"Cool! And yeah: you\'re welcome! I\'ll do what I can!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 33, \"type\": \"setStep\"}, {\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(33,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Hello again, %user.name%!\r\n\r\nDid you find everything?','[{\"text\": \"I have a Poker, Feathers, and a Spider!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 34, \"type\": \"setStep\"}], \"requiredInventory\": \"144:1,160:1,336:1\"}, {\"text\": \"I have the Quintessence, and a Spider!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 34, \"type\": \"setStep\"}], \"requiredInventory\": \"108:1,160:1\"}, {\"text\": \"Not yet...\", \"actions\": [{\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(34,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh, thank you! Hold on one moment...','[{\"text\": \"Okay...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 35, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(35,1,'fullFramePicture',NULL,'sharuminyinka/magic','','[{\"text\": \"Ooh!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 36, \"type\": \"setStep\"}, {\"item\": \"Sharuminyinka\'s Hope\", \"type\": \"receiveItem\", \"description\": \"Sharuminyinka made this for %user.name%.\"}]}]'),(36,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','That\'s harder to do that than it used to be. But I shouldn\'t complain. I\'m honestly so happy. Thank you!','[{\"text\": \"No, that was cool! Thanks!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 37, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(37,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Wonderful!\r\n\r\nAh, I have to go find my brother and tell him! But you and I, we\'ll speak again!','[{\"text\": \"Until then :)\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 38, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(38,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Oh, well, actually, wait. Humans live about 80-100 years...','[{\"text\": \"Uh... yeah, thereabouts...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 39, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(39,1,'dialog','cosmos','sharuminyinka','Right.\r\n\r\nWell. I\'ll try to be quick.\r\n\r\nBut goodbye for now! And thank you again!','[{\"text\": \"Bye...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 40, \"type\": \"setStep\"}, {\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(40,1,'description','cosmos',NULL,'You don\'t hear anything...','[{\"text\": \"Hm...\", \"actions\": [{\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(41,2,'description',NULL,NULL,'You approach the Ant Queen...','[{\"text\": \"Hello. My name is %user.name%.\", \"hideIf\": [\"%user.stat.Bugs Squished%\", \">=\", [\"%user.stat.Bugs Put Outside%\", \"*\", \"2\"]], \"actions\": [{\"step\": 42, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Hello! My name is %user.name%, _enemy_ to all bugs!\", \"hideIf\": [\"%user.stat.Bugs Put Outside%\", \">=\", [\"%user.stat.Bugs Squished%\", \"*\", \"2\"]], \"actions\": [{\"step\": 49, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(42,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv hello, %user.name%. We know you and your pets thvvthvv. You\'ve been relatively friendly to us bugs, at least compared to most humans.\r\n\r\nThvvthvv how can I help you?','[{\"text\": \"I just thought I\'d say \'hello\'.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 43, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(43,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv I see. Excuse my impoliteness thvvthvv. Speaking civilly with humans is not common. But I do appreciate the food you\'ve given my people! Thvvthvv! I would like to offer you something in exchange.','[{\"text\": \"Oh, thanks! That sounds great!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 45, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Oh, that really isn\'t necessary!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 44, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(44,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv I insist!\r\n\r\nBesides, if I\'m being honest, antkind stand to gain from this as well thvvthvv.','[{\"text\": \"Interesting. Tell me more.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 45, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(45,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv yes, I thought you might be interested. It is the plans to a beehive that our allies were able to steal thvvthvv. Many moths died to bring us this information...','[{\"text\": \"Ants and moths are at war with bees?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 46, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(46,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv it depends. But in this case, yes. A new bee empire threatens us all! Thvvthvv! But as we speak, my workers are studying the plans. The geometry thvvthvv. The architecture thvvthvv. We hope to turn this knowledge to our own advantage.','[{\"text\": \"Huh. Why share it with me?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 47, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(47,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv you are observant. Perhaps it is that same keenness that made you aware of our kind thvvthvv. Perhaps that same keenness will enable you to construct a hive from these plans thvvthvv. My workers and I would be very curious to observe that process...','[{\"text\": \"I see. Well, I suppose that\'s a fair deal.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 48, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(48,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','One more thing thvvthvv! Before I give you these plans, you must promise never to squish our kind!','[{\"text\": \"Oh! Of course!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 54, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Ha! I\'ll squish you here and now, and take the plans for myself!\", \"hideIf\": [\"%user.stat.Bugs Put Outside%\", \">=\", [\"%user.stat.Bugs Squished%\", \"*\", \"2\"]], \"actions\": [{\"step\": 53, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(49,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv! We know you well, human! You and your kind are a scourge to all bug kind! Thvvthvv!','[{\"text\": \"As it should be!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 50, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(50,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Wait thvvthvv! I wish to negotiate peace! Thvvthvv. I have brought an offering...','[{\"text\": \"Peace, you say? Tell me more...\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 51, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Sure, I\'ll take that offering... _and squish you here and now!_\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 53, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(51,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv I am queen of but one colony of ants. I cannot guarantee that no centipede, moth, or even ant will ever enter your house again thvvthvv. But if you will agree to never squish a bug again, and instead put them outside, I will give you the blueprints to a beehive thvvthvv.','[{\"text\": \"Very well. I accept your terms.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 54, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"A beehive? What is an ant doing with beehive plans?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 52, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Never! I\'ll squish you here and now, and take the plans for myself!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 53, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(52,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv we acquired them. That is all you need to know.','[{\"text\": \"Very well. I accept your terms.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 54, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"Hmph! I\'ll squish you here and now, and take the plans for myself!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 53, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(53,2,'fullFramePicture',NULL,'stolen-plans/squish','','[{\"text\": \"Another victory.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 55, \"type\": \"setStep\"}, {\"item\": \"Stolen Beehive Plans\", \"type\": \"receiveItem\", \"locked\": true, \"description\": \"%user.name% squished an Ant Queen and took this.\"}, {\"item\": \"Stolen Beehive Plans\", \"type\": \"donateItem\", \"description\": \"%user.name% squished an Ant Queen and took this.\"}, {\"item\": \"Ant Queen\", \"type\": \"loseItem\"}, {\"stat\": \"Bugs Squished\", \"type\": \"incrementStat\"}, {\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(54,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv very well! The plans are yours.\r\n\r\nAs an ally, I caution you: do not go back on your word thvvthvv. The spirits and guardians of antkind have heard your promise.','[{\"text\": \"O-- of course.\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 56, \"type\": \"setStep\"}, {\"item\": \"Stolen Beehive Plans\", \"type\": \"receiveItem\", \"locked\": true, \"description\": \"An Ant Queen gave this to %user.name%.\"}, {\"item\": \"Stolen Beehive Plans\", \"type\": \"donateItem\", \"description\": \"An Ant Queen gave this to %user.name%.\"}, {\"type\": \"setQuestValue\", \"quest\": \"Promised to Not Squish Bugs\", \"value\": 1}, {\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(55,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv your insult will never be forgotten, human! Antkind has nothing to say to you! Thvvthvv!','[{\"text\": \"Hmph!\", \"actions\": [{\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(56,2,'dialog',NULL,'ant-queen','Thvvthvv antkind thanks you, human.','[{\"text\": \"Pas de problème.\", \"actions\": [{\"type\": \"exit\"}]}]'),(57,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','Good day, si--er, ah, human!\r\n\r\nIt seems one of your \\*cough\\* _creatures_ mistook me for a common Fish...\r\n\r\nBut no matter!\r\n\r\nI represent the Nation-state of Tell Samarzhoustia, and on behalf of King Nebuludwigula XIII, I wish to establish a trade route between our people.','[{\"text\": \"Did you cough? (Can fish cough?)\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 58, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"King whonow?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 59, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}, {\"text\": \"I\'d be delighted!\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 60, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(58,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','If they can\'t, but you heard that I did, then one of the two of us has quite a bit of explaining to do.\r\n\r\nNow where was I...\r\n\r\nAh yes: trade!\r\n\r\nThere\'s a river nearby, in which we have established a _very_ secure trade route. Well \\*glances at your pets\\* well it\'s _quite_ secure, you see, and, ah, where was I...\r\n\r\nAh yes: trade!\r\n\r\nProvided you\'ll sign an agreement to trade exclusively with Tell Samarzhoustia for the next one year, we would be happy to absorb the depot construction costs','[{\"text\": \"Would I still be able to use the market?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 61, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(59,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','King Nebuludwigula XIII. Of Tell Samarzhoustia.\r\n\r\n\\*sigh\\* I was warned humans would not know of such things, but...\r\n\r\nOh, uh, where was I?\r\n\r\nAh yes: trade!\r\n\r\nThere\'s a river nearby, in which we have established a _very_ secure trade route. Well \\*glances at your pets\\* well it\'s _quite_ secure, you see, and, ah, where was I...\r\n\r\nAh yes: trade!\r\n\r\nProvided you\'ll sign an agreement to trade exclusively with Tell Samarzhoustia for the next one year, we would be happy to absorb the depot construction costs.','[{\"text\": \"Would I still be able to use the market?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 61, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(60,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','Extraordinary!\r\n\r\nThere\'s a river nearby, in which we have established a _very_ secure trade route. Well \\*glances at your pets\\* well it\'s _quite_ secure, you see, and, ah, where was I...\r\n\r\nAh yes: trade!\r\n\r\nProvided you\'ll sign an agreement to trade exclusively with Tell Samarzhoustia for the next one year, we would be happy to absorb the depot construction costs.','[{\"text\": \"Would I still be able to use the market?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 61, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(61,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','The what now? Market?\r\n\r\nOh!\r\n\r\nOhohohohoho. Yes, yes, that thing. Yes, of course. Your various, ah, human... \\*he waves a flipper\\* whatevers. That won\'t be a problem at all.','[{\"text\": \"Huh. Well. Sure, I guess I\'ll sign?\", \"actions\": [{\"step\": 62, \"type\": \"setStep\"}]}]'),(62,3,'dialog',NULL,'merchant-fish','Wonderful! Wonderful-wonderful!\r\n\r\nYou won\'t regret this, mada--er, human.\r\n\r\nOh, and should your... _creatures_ happen to come home with any other Merchant Fish, the Nation-state of Tell Samarzhoustia would be forever grateful if you could send them our way. Gratitude paid, of course, in trade!','[{\"text\": \"Sounds good.\", \"actions\": [{\"type\": \"exit\"}, {\"type\": \"loseCallingInventory\"}, {\"type\": \"unlockTrader\"}]}]');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `story_section` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

